  import { mapState } from 'vuex'

   mdbFormInline } from 'mdbvue';
  export default {
    name: 'Header',
    components: {
      mdbNavbar,
      mdbNavbarBrand,
      mdbNavbarToggler,
      mdbNavbarNav,
      mdbNavItem,
      mdbDropdown,
      mdbDropdownMenu,
      mdbDropdownToggle,
      mdbDropdownItem,
      mdbInput,
      mdbBtn,
      mdbFormInline,
    },
    computed:{
      ...mapState({
        storeName:'storeName'
      })
    }
  }
</script>
